        <div class="col-xs-12">
            <h1 class="cd-text cd-title">Health badges</h1>
            <p class="cd-text">An important part of our brand, health badges are used to call out the nutritional benefits of a product. There are some geographical variations to take into account that are documented here.</p>

            <h2 class="cd-text cd-title">Health badge types</h2>
            <h3 class="cd-text cd-title">calorie number</h3>
            <p class="cd-text">This health badge must have a value specified for the amount of calories.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="health-badges#0" class="health-badge health-badge--calories">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">130</span>
                    <span class="sr-only">only 130 calories</span>
                </a>
            </p>
